instructions: PUT THE DINNER PLATE ON THE TABLE CLOTH

PUT THE GLASS WATER NEXT TO WINE GLASS

PUT THE DINNER KNIFE ON THE RIGHT NEXT TO THE DINNER PLATE
PUT THE SOUP SPOON NEXT TO DINNER KNIFE ON THE RIGHT&nbsp;<br><br>
